Building and installing shot-boundaries tools
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

Author: Meriem Bendris <m.bendris@gmail.com>


PREREQUISITES
=============

Building opencv-utils requires the following software installed:

    - G++ 4.8 or later
    - ffmpeg or libav development packages: libavcodec-dev, libavformat-dev, libswscale-dev
    - OpenCV 2.4 or later
    - Libconfig 1.4 or later
    - LibXML++2.6 or later




COMPILE
=======
This tool was build on Ubuntu 12.04. You may need to modify the Makefile to adapt to your distribution

    - Basic installation  to "make". Generates binaries on the directory /bin


USE
===
Find how to use the tools in https://github.com/meriembendris/opencv-utils/wiki
